So he must be thin.

15
00:00:49,898 --> 00:00:52,301
By the direction of the mark,
he is a left-handed man.

16
00:00:52,802 --> 00:00:54,597
Master, you are amazing.

17
00:00:55,240 --> 00:00:58,572
I am just as well versed in
the scene trace analysis.

18
