his need for the thrill of committing
a crime is intensifying.

29
00:01:29,250 --> 00:01:31,058
Chief Shen, it's thanks to you

30
00:01:31,280 --> 00:01:33,761
that this street is so safe and secure.

31
00:01:33,912 --> 00:01:35,504
You're really good at flattering me.

32
00:01:55,970 --> 00:01:56,866
Chief Shen.

33
