Come on.

34
00:01:59,560 --> 00:02:00,210
Coming.

35
00:02:21,730 --> 00:02:24,504
You are a persistent and earnest lady.

36
00:02:24,810 --> 00:02:27,000
I hope

37
00:02:27,120 --> 00:02:28,522
you don't end up like your father.

38
00:02:32,120 --> 00:02:34,296
What's the matter, master?

39
00:02:35,410 --> 00:02:36,053
Nothing.

40
00:02:41,594 --> 00:02:42,512
Li Xinghe.

41
00:02:42,770 --> 00:02:43,730
There you are.

42
00:02:49,522 --> 00:02:50,296
Li Xinghe.

43
00:02:53,480 --> 00:02:54,373
What happened?

44
00:02:54,560 --> 00:02:55,672
Were they attacked?

45
00:02:55,722 --> 00:02:56,613
What about Yao Zhan?

46
00:03:05,093 --> 00:03:05,584
Hey.

47
00:03:05,853 --> 00:03:06,410
Hey.

48
00:03:06,581 --> 00:03:07,581
Get up and drink your medicine.

49
00:03:08,080 --> 00:03:09,677
Yao Zhan, run!

50
00:03:11,328 --> 00:03:12,176
It's okay.

51
00:03:12,437 --> 00:03:14,224
I'm your father. I'm here.

52
00:03:19,845 --> 00:03:22,657
Why do you have so many wrinkles

53
00:03:22,797 --> 00:03:24,765
at such a young age?

54
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:29,192
Master.

55
00:03:29,640 --> 00:03:30,690
I'm here to deliver his medicine

56
00:03:30,808 --> 00:03:33,154
and take his pulse.

57
00:03:33,912 --> 00:03:34,989
Do you also how to take a pulse?

58
00:03:36,640 --> 00:03:37,525
I can learn.

59
00:03:38,605 --> 00:03:39,621
Is he still unconscious?

60
00:03:40,122 --> 00:03:40,954
Yes.

61
00:03:42,370 --> 00:03:43,808
Did you find Yao Zhan?

62
00:03:44,370 --> 00:03:45,872
I looked for him, but no luck.

63
00:03:46,885 --> 00:03:47,824
I guess

64
00:03:48,162 --> 00:03:49,541
we'll just have to wait
until he wakes up

65
00:03:50,296 --> 00:03:51,746
and ask him what's going on.

66
00:03:52,888 --> 00:03:53,365
Okay.

67
00:03:54,600 --> 00:03:55,080
So

68
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:57,792
if there's nothing else, I'll go
back to Court of Judicial Review.

69
00:04:00,112 --> 00:04:01,464
Goodbye, master.

70
00:04:03,370 --> 00:04:04,184
Shen Mei!

71
00:04:04,690 --> 00:04:06,000
Shen Mei!

72
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:07,440
Is Shen Mei home?

73
00:04:09,045 --> 00:04:09,706
Official Chu.

74
00:04:10,034 --> 00:04:10,968
What's wrong?

75
00:04:11,210 --> 00:04:13,690
Shen Mei's uncle said that she
never returned to the pharmacy

76
00:04:13,720 --> 00:04:15,376
after she left to deliver
the medicine in the afternoon.

77
00:04:15,810 --> 00:04:16,850
Her uncle went out to find her,

78
00:04:16,906 --> 00:04:18,280
but still couldn't find her either.

79
00:04:19,080 --> 00:04:20,210
Did she not come home?

80
00:04:20,378 --> 00:04:20,920
No.

81
00:04:21,122 --> 00:04:22,765
I haven't seen Shen Mei back.

82
