Yes, Mei hasn't been home all day.

83
00:04:27,890 --> 00:04:30,101
Where could she go
at this time of night?

84
00:04:31,690 --> 00:04:33,120
Let's go out and find.

85
00:04:33,392 --> 00:04:35,970
Shen Mei!

86
00:04:37,410 --> 00:04:38,968
Shen Mei!

87
00:04:38,992 --> 00:04:40,877
Mei is not taken by
the bad guys, is she?

88
00:04:40,936 --> 00:04:43,520
Stop talking nonsense and go find her.

89
00:04:43,701 --> 00:04:44,520
Shen Mei!

90
00:04:44,578 --> 00:04:45,120
Hurry up.

91
00:04:45,520 --> 00:04:46,093
Official Chu.

92
00:04:46,541 --> 00:04:47,170
Did you find her?

93
00:04:47,229 --> 00:04:48,754
I've searched over there,
but no findings.

94
00:04:49,133 --> 00:04:49,706
Keep looking.

95
00:04:49,802 --> 00:04:50,221
Yes.

96
00:04:53,576 --> 00:04:54,245
No way.

97
00:04:55,080 --> 00:04:56,410
It can't be her.

98
00:04:56,480 --> 00:04:57,330
Shen Mei!

99
00:05:19,010 --> 00:05:19,938
You know what?

100
00:05:20,280 --> 00:05:21,474
When you were giving me the medicine,

101
